article_text:
Kankakee, IL (60901)

Today

Thunderstorms likely this morning. Then the chance of scattered thunderstorms this afternoon. High around 80F. Winds S at 10 to 20 mph. Chance of rain 80%..

Tonight

Scattered thunderstorms during the evening. Cloudy skies after midnight. Low 67F. Winds S at 10 to 15 mph. Chance of rain 60%.
